trans-unit.source: Provides data for a focus-changed event.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller data för en händelse med fokus ändras.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationFocusChangedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.AutomationFocusChangedEventArgs"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The `idObject` and `idChild` parameters contain the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_aa](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] object identifiers that UI Automation clients can use to link an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> to an `IAccessible` object in an older accessible technology application.
trans-unit.target: Den `idObject` och `idChild` parametrar innehålla den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_aa](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] objekt-ID som en UI Automation-klienter kan använda för att länka en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>till ett `IAccessible` objekt i ett äldre program hjälpmedelsteknik.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_id](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-id-md.md)] of the object that received focus.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_id](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-id-md.md)] hos det objekt som tagits emot fokus.

trans-unit.source: The child [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-id-md.md)] of the object that received focus.
trans-unit.target: Underordnat [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-id-md.md)] hos det objekt som tagits emot fokus.

trans-unit.source: Gets the child [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_aa](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] identifier of the object receiving focus.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar underordnat [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_aa](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] identifierare för det objekt som får fokus.

trans-unit.source: Object [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] are 32-bit values that identify categories of accessible objects within an application.
trans-unit.target: Objektet [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] är 32-bitars värden som identifierar kategorier av tillgängliga objekt i ett program.

trans-unit.source: The `idObject` and `idChild` parameters contain the object [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] that clients can use to link an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> to an `IAccessible` object in an older accessible technology application.
trans-unit.target: Den `idObject` och `idChild` parametrar innehåller objektet [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] som klienter kan använda för att länka en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>till ett `IAccessible` objekt i ett äldre program hjälpmedelsteknik.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_id](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-id-md.md)] of the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_aa](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] object that generated the event.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_id](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-id-md.md)] av den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_aa](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] -objektet som genererade händelsen.

trans-unit.source: Object [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] are 32-bit values that identify categories of accessible objects within an application.
trans-unit.target: Objektet [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] är 32-bitars värden som identifierar kategorier av tillgängliga objekt i ett program.

trans-unit.source: The `idObject` and `idChild` parameters contain the object [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] that clients can use to link an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> to an `IAccessible` object in an older accessible technology application.
trans-unit.target: Den `idObject` och `idChild` parametrar innehåller objektet [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] som klienter kan använda för att länka en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>till ett `IAccessible` objekt i ett äldre program hjälpmedelsteknik.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-id-md.md)] of the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] element that is receiving focus.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-id-md.md)] av den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] element som tar emot fokus.

trans-unit.source: For possible values, see [Object Identifiers](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/msaa/msaaccrf_5q05.asp) in the Microsoft Active Accessibility documentation.
trans-unit.target: Möjliga värden finns i [objektidentifierare](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/msaa/msaaccrf_5q05.asp) i Microsoft Active Accessibility-dokumentationen.
